# Production Centrale Bourse — VPS IP publique
# Sur le serveur : cp deploy/env.production.13.140.137.171.example .env
# Puis compléter MYSQL_PASSWORD et SECRET_KEY, redémarrer l'API.

DB_ENGINE=mysql
MYSQL_HOST=127.0.0.1
MYSQL_PORT=3306
MYSQL_DATABASE=brvm_agent
MYSQL_USER=centrale_bourse
MYSQL_PASSWORD=CHANGEZ_MOI

SECRET_KEY=CHANGEZ_MOI_GENERER_AVEC_python3_import_secrets

# Origine du site (sans /api à la fin)
CORS_ORIGINS=http://13.140.137.171:8080

FLASK_DEBUG=false

REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379/0

GUNICORN_BIND=127.0.0.1:5051
GUNICORN_WORKERS=3
GUNICORN_THREADS=2

DISABLE_SCRAPE_SCHEDULER=true
SCRAPE_ON_STARTUP=false
ALLOW_LIVE_QUOTE_FETCH=false
PALMARES_ON_STARTUP=true

PAYMENTS_ENABLED=false
NEWS_USE_DATABASE=true

HOME_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=120
LISTED_COMPANIES_CACHE_TTL=300
ANALYSIS_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=1800
COMPARE_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=300
RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=120

TRIAL_DURATION_DAYS=5
MAX_WATCHLIST_ITEMS=50
MAX_PRICE_ALERTS=20
